{"tid":602932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"古代軍隊對現代軍隊邊個會贏？","createTime":"2018-03-23T10:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T11:11:56.000Z","uid":155642,"like":0,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"953eac93c59e9125f74d6bf2e0077a4266724c82","tid":602932,"uid":155642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:01:37.000Z","msg":"古代有好多近戰兵器同出名嘅戰略同兵法，可以不動一兵一卒戰勝對手，同時古人有一種好強大嘅信念，好多士兵都係為國而戰，死都唔會放棄同投降，毅力驚人，好難會被動搖。<br />\n<br />\n現今科技發達，軍用武器先進，有導彈、坦克、熗等等，甚至飛機，可以遙距遠處殺敵。<br />\n<br />\n但係兵法呢樣野係玩心理戰，只要令到敵人嘅心理出現混亂，令到近戰古人有優勢。<br />\n<br />\n不過我都係覺得現代軍隊贏緊，因為一枝機熗或者派個無人機都可以橫掃對手啦屌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地又覺得呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63dc2784bc96d31200d43e37d0dd9f8b01d71f2","tid":602932,"uid":25126,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:02:42.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"789e5cebb4c059de650492c713c4d78ae6367efb","tid":602932,"uid":31314,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:10:11.000Z","msg":"現代軍隊攞架飛機掟粒炸彈都贏硬啦<br />\n問嚟都on9"},{"pid":"7cd3d7fa81be85f8c4893b58cb0e0b4d6a3101ca","tid":602932,"uid":12923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:11:51.000Z","msg":"On99"},{"pid":"18fe2fd51a08e5c052f2fafcd6480590c91de93c","tid":602932,"uid":22999,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:12:45.000Z","msg":"建議你去驗下腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13b3a8b61cef8d94b40acda736ef0e5c27e00e29","tid":602932,"uid":61082,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:14:14.000Z","msg":"有冇規模，年代，國家？<br />\n<br />\n十個羅馬帝國軍團（六萬人）<br />\n一個現代美軍步兵師（一萬五千人）<br />\n<br />\n正面對決嘅話我諗唔到羅馬點贏<br />\n<br />\n一個美軍步兵師唔講啲咩其他迫擊砲榴彈砲嗰啲裝備，淨係坦克已經有兩百幾架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n碌住過去都碌到羅馬元老院"},{"pid":"4c55f81c44c2a586a89bcf4122099c8aa3d8448c","tid":602932,"uid":43886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:22:37.000Z","msg":"冷兵器對熱兵器有討論價值？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ac1fc11d72f47cfe350d75c4340ee40c529b63","tid":602932,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:24:10.000Z","msg":"弱智"},{"pid":"6848da862574cbec5ef23248c71d311f3c8d7688","tid":602932,"uid":162713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:26:43.000Z","msg":"古代打仗好多時死三四成 就潰不成軍啦<br />\n死戰？ 咪玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdf312b8921833d05a4f460aa6c6c59896a08b3","tid":602932,"uid":42679,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:30:55.000Z","msg":"小學雞睇完烏干達黑豹就以為冷兵器鬥得贏槍炮導彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34fd4fc0ea83c0374e90583c423a6225afe20ede","tid":602932,"uid":13782,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:33:31.000Z","msg":"清朝同外國人打既仗應該可以借鑑下，差距應該仲少啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c5d0ad420b1e82b23f81864faa5b6cabc06946","tid":602932,"uid":38623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:34:54.000Z","msg":"分分鐘一架坦克都清場"},{"pid":"69af15fa4e4e02dafbb96bcb9be5112a603887ee","tid":602932,"uid":3254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:36:28.000Z","msg":"用屎腦諗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48af9aa78674dd9dcc94